* Median of an array of numbers
*
* 计算数组中所有数字的中位数
*
* @category Math
*
* @param numbers - The array of numbers to calculate the median. 要计算中位数的数字数组
* @returns The median of the numbers. 数组中所有数字的中位数
*
* @example
* ```ts
* median([1, 2, 3, 4, 5]) // => 3
* median([1, 2, 3, 4]) // => 2.5
* median([]) // => NaN
* ```
